🔷 Status Codes

| Code | Meaning      |
| ---- | ------------ |
| 200  | Success      |
| 201  | Created      |
| 400  | Bad Request  |
| 404  | Not Found    |
| 500  | Server Error |

Example:

```javascript
res.status(201).json(newUser);
```

---

🔷 Middleware in API

```javascript
app.use((req, res, next) => {
  console.log(req.method, req.url);
  next();
});
```

